{"tid":38312,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"武漢男外出買菜半小時　回來驚見房子遭夷平","createTime":"2016-12-14T00:12:14.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-14T01:22:33.000Z","uid":23707,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"69313b1cacaa16f10b97b783cb1f4f1ba996c2d3","tid":38312,"uid":23707,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-14T00:12:14.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/cn/bkn/cnt/news/20161214/bkncn-20161214013932723-1214_05011_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fcn%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20161214%2Fbkncn-20161214013932723-1214_05011_001.html&d=XRlc7p3co2%2BBWC6nCTdE7XvMcj1OveTHk6NUHU39nRk%3D&h=1c2a1883\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/cn/bkn/cnt/news/20161214/bkncn-20161214013932723-1214_05011_001.html</a><br />\n<br />\n【<a href=\"http://on.cc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fon.cc&d=XRlc7p3co2%2BBWC6nCTdE7XvMcj1OveTHk6NUHU39nRk%3D&h=09d9f3e5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">on.cc</a>東網專訊】內地再發生強拆事件，湖北武漢一名熊姓男子上周五（9日）早上出門到市場買菜，不料來回才半個小時，房子已被人夷為平地。熊男事後質問負責交涉的村委會，對方卻表示，事前已知會熊男的家人，雙方已談妥清拆事宜。 <br />\n<br />\n據熊男透露，近日武漢航發集團要在他房子附近修建高速公路，惟該集團並未派人與他討論清拆的事宜，只是委任村委會出面處理。至於房子被拆遷，他事前亦未收到任何通知。熊男又表示，自己經謍藥材買賣的生意，房子被強拆後，大批藥材亦被埋在瓦礫底下，單是這批貨物，便令他損失逾7萬元（人民幣‧下同）。另外還有生活用品、電器、衣物等等，價值更難以估算。 <br />\n<br />\n惟村委會書記表示，十多天前已通知對方家人將財物搬走，在進行清拆時，熊男家中已沒有甚麼東西，只剩下一些酒在二樓。而清拆的前一天，村委會亦已通知熊男的母親與舅舅，雙方在口頭上達成協議。書記又強調，村委會會賠償熊男所損失的酒，並會給熊男「過渡費」，讓他在外面找到地方租住。 <br />\n<br />\n事件強起網民熱議，有人質疑「誰都通知就不通知屋主，這也叫通知嗎」、「舅舅憑甚麼為屋主作主」；亦有人對政府冷嘲熱諷，稱「會拆敢拆才是國家的好幹部」、「這姓熊的肯定是外國派來擾亂社會秩序的間諜」<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 、「看到我國的發展速度驚人，真是感到安慰」。"},{"pid":"14132cd33401903c33771122e3e0bbafe58a056e","tid":38312,"uid":6981,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-14T00:14:25.000Z","msg":"強國<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"129998bf02d98eeeb52e61c6c4744388af54a66d","tid":38312,"uid":21028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-14T00:16:10.000Z","msg":"還有黨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"33213ca81d8ea4f2bb2395fc33f59b310b4b4f6f","tid":38312,"uid":54344,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-14T00:16:57.000Z","msg":"蚹"},{"pid":"cc3c5c5a8bf51566e59e510a0fb4dc3c381e4b63","tid":38312,"uid":35410,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-14T00:18:46.000Z","msg":"殘國特色收地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8aa46671a0494546f726164ad16d9b20f521fa66","tid":38312,"uid":20943,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-14T00:20:52.000Z","msg":"啱呀"},{"pid":"ca27222aef34dfa3d9941b6ceba34a32f9aff4e4","tid":38312,"uid":49588,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-14T00:28:22.000Z","msg":"內你支那老母臭西！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n中國大陸！<br />\n亦即係鄰國，地獄鬼國，"},{"pid":"78e1b9e2c439537a7a28b23aadd20ca190b4af95","tid":38312,"uid":7323,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-14T00:29:42.000Z","msg":"妨礙中國發展，拆"},{"pid":"1772a187e06e6db00d45a582e01f5e9bea143a6b","tid":38312,"uid":32325,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-14T00:32:11.000Z","msg":"每日一笑話<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"12a87fd006f9ca34e443ce8eebadd36ca65e7067","tid":38312,"uid":30169,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-14T00:35:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/42.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3953e22aa985180e9f803de3ebf107750393d5c6","tid":38312,"uid":23707,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-14T00:37:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>內你支那老母臭西！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n中國大陸！<br />\n亦即係鄰國，地獄鬼國，</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n東網就由佢啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"04d5b076bd3edac8f838bdc3dbcb943cb4345aed","tid":38312,"uid":42611,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"